FBIS4-5853 "dreas072_a_94002" FBIS-EAS-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Officials Preview U.S. Secretary Perry's Visit Officials Preview U.S. Secretary Perry's Visit OW1404090194 Tokyo KYODO in English 0846 GMT 14 Apr 94 OW1404090194 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, April 14 KYODO -- U.S. Defense Secretary William Perry will visit Japan from April 19 to 21 to hold talks with the prime minister and foreign minister, Foreign Ministry officials said Thursday. Perry, who will fly to Tokyo from Seoul, will also meet with the Defense Agency chief, the officials said. He is expected to discuss problems involving North Korea's alleged development of nuclear weapons and the Japan-U.S. security arrangement, they said. He may also inspect U.S. forces during his stay, they said.
